c: 2
v: 233
t: "Jibim…ďe …ďen yo muynin …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen duu…ďi …ói…ói timmu…ói; wonannde on faandii…óo timminde muyninngol ngol.No fawii jibinanaa…óo on, √Īammingol holitinira [rew…ďe] …ďen no mo∆ī∆īiri. WoŇčkii woo fawaaka si wanaa ko ki waawata. Wata jibin…óo on lorrire sabu …ďi…ó…óo makko on, wanaa jibinanaa…óo on kadi lorrirtee sabu …ďi…ó…óo makko on; no fawii ronoowo on yeru …óum. Si …ďe faandike entude e hoore yarlondiral hakkunde ma…ď…ďe e diisondiral, bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe. Si on faandike …óa…ď…ďude muyninanoowo on …ďi…ó…ďe mon …ďen, bakkaatu fawaakii on, si on jonnirii kon ko …ďen [muyninoo…ďe] hanndi e mo∆ī∆īere.Hulee Alla, nganndon ko O Reenu…óo kala ko golloton"